    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Weather on the Web</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Letter by Richard Ellenson responds to June 1 article on weather news available on Internet; says his favorite site is www.wunderground.com</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''All the Weather You'll Ever Need'' (June 1): I use only the Web site www.wunderground.com for all my weather. Not only does it load faster than www.weather.com, but it gives a more detailed look at the weather for any town.</p>
        <p>RICHARD ELLENSON  Tenafly, N.J.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
